## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="08b78-179">Jeśli <xref:System.Data.ParameterDirection> jest wyjścia i wykonanie skojarzonego <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> nie zwraca wartości <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter> zawiera wartość null.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="08b78-179">If the <xref:System.Data.ParameterDirection> is output, and execution of the associated <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> does not return a value, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter> contains a null value.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="08b78-180">`Output`, `InputOut`, i `ReturnValue` Parametry zwracane przez wywołanie metody <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand.ExecuteReader%2A> będą niedostępne do czasu wywołania <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.Close%2A> na <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="08b78-180">`Output`, `InputOut`, and `ReturnValue` parameters returned by calling <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand.ExecuteReader%2A> cannot be accessed until you call <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.Close%2A> on the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="08b78-181">Poniższy przykład tworzy <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter> i ustawia niektóre jego właściwości.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="08b78-181">The following example creates a <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter> and sets some of its properties.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Public Sub CreateOracleDbParameter()  
   Dim parameter As New OracleParameter()  
   parameter.ParameterName = "pDName"  
   parameter.DbType = DbType.String  
   parameter.Value = "ENGINEERING"  
   parameter.SourceColumn = "DName"  
End Sub  
```  
  
